global-borderRadius-0.description: Example: rounding of components, like buttons and cards

global-boxShadow-0.description: Example: shadows of cards and other components

global-fontSize-base.description: The base fontsize that impacts all other font sizes (example: base*1.2)

global-opacity-0.description: Example: opacity standards for surfaces but also the color of shadows

global-space-0.description: Example: padding between elements and components
